Class Sprite

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Sprite

  • public class Sprite
extends Object
    A sprite represents the model of an entity on the screen. It has a position in X and Y coordinates, a certain velocity in a direction expressed by X and Y coordinates, A width and a height, and an image to draw on the screen.
    Author:
    Clinton Cao, Dmity Malarev, Matthijs Halvemaan, Sunwei Wang, Michiel Doesburg.
